A script to create the necessary tables can be found in:

  ${EGDIR}/DATABASE.mysql

For regular database maintenance, add the following crontab entry:

  0 * * * * ${BINDIR}/cleanup -c ${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}/policyd.conf

